  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen credibility factors evaluated at Model Risk Level 2. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; hasContextOfUse is intentionally absent, leaving intended-use scope undefined (W-ON-01).",
